    <%= f.radio_button :management_team_filled_roles, 'Supply Chain' %> Supply Chain
  </div><br>

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="exampleInputName2">What country is the management team based in?*</label>
    <%= f.text_field :management_city_location, class: "form-control" %>
  </div><br>

  <div class="form-group">
    <label>How is your past experience relevant to the problem your company is solving?*</label>
    <%= f.radio_button :past_experience_relevancy,'I can’t believe no one else spotted this opportunity; we are getting up to speed as fast as we can!',:checked => true %> I can’t believe no one else spotted this opportunity; we are getting up to speed as fast as we can!<br>
    <%= f.radio_button :past_experience_relevancy,'We are recognized industry experts'%> We are recognized industry experts<br>
    <%= f.radio_button :past_experience_relevancy,'It’s a new industry but we’ve seen the same problem before in a different context'%> It’s a new industry but we’ve seen the same problem before in a different context<br>
    <%= f.radio_button :past_experience_relevancy,'It’s a new industry but the problem aligns with our strengths as a management team'%> It’s a new industry but the problem aligns with our strengths as a management team 
  </div><br>

  <div class="form-check">
    <label>How much time is your management team spending on the idea?*</label>
    <%= f.radio_button :management_spending, 'We’re testing the waters on an idea',:checked => true%> We’re testing the waters on an idea<br> 
    <%= f.radio_button :management_spending, 'The co-founders are full time, but everyone else is part time'%> The co-founders are full time, but everyone else is part time<br>
    <%= f.radio_button :management_spending, 'The entire management team is full time'%> The entire management team is full time<br>
    <%= f.radio_button :management_spending, 'We’re only working on this in our spare time until it makes sense to quit our day jobs'%> We’re only working on this in our spare time until it makes sense to quit our day jobs
  </div><br>

  <div class="form-check">
    <label>How many full-time employees have you hired?*</label>
    <%= f.radio_button :full_time_employees, 'None',:checked => true%> None<br>
    <%= f.radio_button :full_time_employees, '1 - 5'%> 1 - 5<br>
    <%= f.radio_button :full_time_employees, '5 - 10'%> 5 - 10<br>
    <%= f.radio_button :full_time_employees, '>10'%> >10 
  </div><br>

  <div class="form-check">
    <label>How much experience does your management team have working at early-stage companies?*</label>
    <%= f.radio_button :early_stage_experience, 'We’ve just graduated from school',:checked => true%> We’ve just graduated from school<br>
    <%= f.radio_button :early_stage_experience,'Each of us has worked at a startup before'%> Each of us has worked at a startup before<br>
    <%= f.radio_button :early_stage_experience, 'We mainly have experience in larger companies'%> We mainly have experience in larger companies<br>
    <%= f.radio_button :early_stage_experience,'We’ve successfully built multiple companies'%> We’ve successfully built multiple companies<br>
    <%= f.radio_button :early_stage_experience, 'One of us has some experience at a startup'%> One of us has some experience at a startup<br>
  </div><br>

  <div class="form-check">
    <label>What is the management team’s relationship to the country you operate in?*</label>
    <%= f.radio_button :management_team_relationship, 'We’re transplants but have lived here for some time',:checked => true %> We’re transplants but have lived here for some time<br>
    <%= f.radio_button :management_team_relationship,'We’re from here' %> We’re from here<br>
    <%= f.radio_button :management_team_relationship,'We’re from the region' %> We’re from the region<br>
    <%= f.radio_button :management_team_relationship, 'We came to the area specifically to launch our business' %> We came to the area specifically to launch our business<br>
  </div><br>

  <div class="form-check">
    <label>How much has the management team invested into the company?*</label>
    <%= f.radio_button :management_team_invest,'We’ve had early successes, in incubators, accelerators or with grants and other sources of funding, so we didn’t need to invest our own capital in the business', :checked => true %> We’ve had early successes, in incubators, accelerators or with grants and other sources of funding, so we didn’t need to invest our own capital in the business<br>
    <%= f.radio_button :management_team_invest,'We didn’t have much to contribute financially, but our network (including friends and family) has helped us get started'%> We didn’t have much to contribute financially, but our network (including friends and family) has helped us get started<br>
    <%= f.radio_button :management_team_invest,'We haven’t needed much capital yet'%> We haven’t needed much capital yet<br>
    <%= f.radio_button :management_team_invest,'The sacrifice has been considerable—we gave up great jobs and put everything we had into the business'%> The sacrifice has been considerable—we gave up great jobs and put everything we had into the business<br> 
  </div><br>

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="exampleInputName2">How much per month does the management team earn in salary and other benefits?*<br>
    Please enter in U.S. $ equivalent</label>
    <%= f.number_field :management_earnings, class: "form-control"%>
  </div><br>

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="comment">If you weren't working on this business, what would you be doing?*</label>
    <%= f.text_area :not_working_with_business, class: "form-control", row: "10"%>
  </div><br>
  
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="comment">WORK & MANAGEMENT STYLE<hr>What are you most passionate about?*</label>
    <%= f.text_area :management_passionate, class: "form-control", row: "10"%>
  </div><br>

